# First make sure we normalise all line endings to LF in the repository.
# N.B. [2] claims that this substitutes for core.autocrlf ...
# N.B. [3] has an argument against this global setting.
*       text=auto

# Experiment with trying LF for all source files.
*       text eol=lf
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.png   binary
